data.description: RARE FIND! GREAT TERRAIN VALUE WITH $15,000 SELLER CREDIT TOWARD BUYER’S RATE BUYDOWN, CLOSING COSTS OR PREPAIDS!! South-facing, corner lot! Curb appeal galore, beautiful architecture, great exterior paint choices, wraparound porch. Inviting two-story entry with welcoming vibe! Crisp, stylish, no expense spared. Boasts a modern farmhouse flair with rustic wood-look tile and high-end carpet. Flexible living room space to use as you see fit. Formal dining room is flooded with light and can easily seat six. Family room includes custom shiplap and tile fireplace/TV wall and has ideal interaction with the cheery gourmet kitchen! Custom finished cabinetry, bead board backsplash, granite counters and large farm sink, it’s a fun space! Newer Whirlpool appliance suite with an armoire refrigerator, gas cooktop, double ovens and dishwasher with stainless tub! Colorful bead board island seats two, has quartz counter, plenty of prep and storage space. Kitchen nook has direct access to the back deck. Zeroscaped back yard, quality turf and flagstone patio redone in 2022. Cottage-style powder room. Laundry room leads to the oversized, 3 car tandem garage. Upstairs, the architecturally stunning, huge primary bedroom is private, fit for a king and more. En-suite bathroom is stylish with blue cabinetry, quartz counter, black fixtures and metal mirrors against shiplap backdrop. Large, oval soaking tub and shower with seat. Spacious loft is ideal sitting area for the primary bedroom or great study space, play area or easy to enclose as another bedroom. Two secondary bedrooms finish off the upper level and share an updated, cutely outfitted hall bathroom with quartz counter, one sink and tub/shower combo. Garden level basement adds 1,000+ square feet of permitted, finished space! Fresh carpeting throughout, considerable family room, large bedroom and huge bonus room which could be used as theater, game room or study! Three-quarter bath and mechanical room with new 50 gallon water heater!
